name: "Winter, 2009" - Limited Edition of 25 Prints by Ben Roberts
description:
Limited Edition Photographic Print by Ben Roberts. 

This image was taken on New Years Day 2009 on Cannock Chase, Staffordshire, UK. Britain was in the grip of an unprecedented period of cold weather. 


11x14" Print - (image size 13x8.6" with white border)

Edition of 25 - Archival Digital C-Type Print on Fuji Crystal Archive Matt Paper.

name: "Room Service" - Limited Edition of 5 Prints by Ben Roberts
description:
"Room Service" By Ben Roberts

This image was taken in Bournemouth in 2007; It's part of a small body of work that was selected for the Jen Bekman Gallery "Hey Hot Shot" competition. 

Limited Edition of 5 Archival Lambda Prints, printed by master printer John Cleur at Argento, London. 

20x16" print (image area 19x14.8" with a white border)

Price includes shipping.

name: "Calle Ojos Del Salado, Granada, 2007" - Limited Edition of 5 Prints by Ben Roberts
description:
"Calle Ojos Del Salado, Granada, 2007" By Ben Roberts

This image is from a body of work entitled "The Brick Business" that covers the environmental and social effects of the construction boom that is occurring on Spain's Mediterranean coastline. This series has recently been shortlisted for the British Journal of Photography's "Project Assistance Awards".

Limited Edition of 5 Archival Lambda Prints, printed by master printer John Cleur at Argento, London. 

20x16" print (image area 19x5" with a white border)

Price includes shipping.
